02.Filesystem            Size  Used Avail Use% Mounted on  
03./dev/mapper/vg_centos-lv_root  
04.                       50G   14G   34G  30% /  
05.tmpfs                 1.9G     0  1.9G   0% /dev/shm  
06./dev/sda1             485M   37M  423M   8% /boot  


2、从新设定vg_home-lv_home的大小 




[plain] view plaincopyprint? 
